{"tid":1161411,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過痾屎/尿嗰陣硬係痾唔曬","createTime":"2019-05-19T07:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T07:33:21.000Z","uid":163524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce83d169fdcdf5905454ed548888e0a1269f378","tid":1161411,"uid":163524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"屙尿嗰陣就硬係剩低最尾一下屙唔出屙唔曬<br />\n一丘返條褲佢又自己痾返出嚟<br />\n有時候都幾大灘下....<br />\n<br />\n啱啱痾屎又係咁<br />\n硬係好似未屙晒<br />\n但係屙又屙唔出<br />\n咁於是乎就放棄<br />\n一敏屎嗰陣張紙巾就敏到一撻啡色<br />\n即係啱啱其實係有嚿屎已經屙到肛門邊<br />\n但係又出唔到嚟<br />\n<br />\n真係幾撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710a3fd7acaa06c596a4325b2353e8cef5533aff","tid":1161411,"uid":242573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:30:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84a61798c1a2c02ae92325b7218cfb104609ae54","tid":1161411,"uid":235684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}